#### Publications and Resources

The history and development of Kelvinside Academy are documented in several publications, including "Kelvinside Academy, 1878–1978" by Colin Mackay, "Kelvinside Academy, 1878–1923" by William Brodie, and "Kelvinside Academy, 1878–1928" by David Morrice Low. The school also publishes "Minerva," a termly newsletter that keeps the community informed.

